--------------------------------------------
STEP 11: Update Employee Salary
--------------------------------------------

Incorrect Command:
UPDATE employees WHERE id = 1;

Error:
ERROR 1064 (42000): SQL syntax error

Correct Command:
UPDATE employees
SET salary = 60000
WHERE id = 2;

Output:
Query OK, 1 row affected
Rows matched: 1  Changed: 1


